    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine Service, Model Year 1994 - 1998 - CRANKCASE, CRANKSHAFT, CONNECTING
        RODS AND PISTONS - Flywheel and Housing - Check Flywheel Housing Face Runout
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="test" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Check Flywheel Housing Face Runout</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Keep the crankshaft end play at zero in the same direction for all measurements.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Attach a dial indicator magnetic base to the crankshaft and place the indicator tip against
                housing face.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Measure at four points 90&#176; apart for a total face variation. Refer to the specification
                for the housing face runout tolerance.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
